					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">nestopia calls it "NANJING, Mapper 163"
<br />
<br />edit:LC3664BML-10 is 64K of RAM
<br />CY6264-70SC is  8K of RAM
<br />and 29LV160BTC-90 appears to be a 16M-BIT flash rom  (16 megabits =2 megabytes)
<br />
<br />so it would be the CHR-RAM, SRAM, and then PRG ROM  
<br />
<br />It would appear you only have one ROM to replace and the one built in may be reprogrammable.
<br />
<br />edit:nestopia confirms it uses chr-ram</div>

					
